body.description: It’s time to Tampax and live your life without limits. Get incredible all day comfort and protection for up to eight hours with Tampax Pearl tampons. Choose from five different absorbencies to match your changing flow. Got leaks? Go up an absorbency. Uncomfortable to remove? Go down an absorbency. Designed with a LeakGuard Braid to help stop leaks before they happen. Tampax Pearl Super Plus Absorbency provides protection you can feel good about. Free of dyes, perfume, latex, BPA, and elemental chlorine bleaching. Plus, inserting the tampon is made easy thanks to the applicator’s Anti-Slip Grip, while Tampax FormFit protection lets it gently expand to your individual shape. Ready to ditch the leaks? Get amazing protection with Tampax, the #1 U.S. Gynecologist recommended tampon brand. Discover your perfect flow combo and get the protection you need. natural rubber latex based on 2020 survey

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Find your Flow Combo If your tampon leaks just after a few hours, try going up an absorbency size for better comfort and protection*. Simply go up from Light to Regular or from your current size up to the next higher absorbency. Only Tampax Pearl tampons have five absorbencies so you can find your flow combo. *Use the lowest absorbency that meets your needs Find your Flow Combo If your tampon is uncomfortable to remove, go down for a lighter absorbency*. Choose the right tampon absorbency throughout your period for better comfort and protection. Simply go down from Ultra to Super Plus or from your current size down to the next lightest absorbency. *Use the lowest absorbency that meets your needs

Outstanding Protection with Tampax Pearl LeakGuard Braid Tampax Pearl tampons feature a LeakGuard Braid that helps stop leaks by channeling them back into the core. Controlled Insertion The Anti-Slip Grip lets you hold the applicator securely, so you can insert the tampon with its rounded tip comfortably and easily. Smooth Removal Layer A smooth layer makes for easy tampon removal and outstanding comfort during your period. FormFit Protection FormFit design gently expands to fit your individual shape, so you can feel comfortable and confident during your period.

Frequently Asked Questions How does Tampax Pearl feel different than other tampons? Tampax Pearl Tampons have a special LeakGuard Braid to help stop leaks before they happen, while a Smooth Removal Layer allows for easy removal. Plus, FormFit Protection gently expands to fit your individual shape. How long can I wear a tampon? You can wear a tampon for up to eight hours, but never leave it in for longer than that. If you usually sleep longer, set an alarm or just use a pad instead. How do I know which absorbency to use? Choosing the right tampon absorbency can make a big difference to be comfortable and avoid leaks. Take the Tampax Quiz on Tampax's website to learn more. What makes Tampax Pearl different from Tampax Pocket Pearl? Both Tampax Pearl and Tampax Pocket Pearl offer outstanding protection with a LeakGuard Braid to help prevent leaks. The main difference is that Tampax Pocket Pearl is compact in size so it fits in your pocket. When ready to use, extend the compact applicator to make it a full-size one.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great at absorbing but not the most comfortable.
reviews.reviewText: Tampax Super Plus Tampons are designed for heavy flow days, and they deliver on their promise of superior absorption. They can handle even the heaviest of flows, providing peace of mind and allowing me to carry on with my day without disruptions.The most glaring issue with Tampax Super Plus Tampons is their level of comfort, or rather, the lack thereof. Despite their impressive absorbency, wearing these tampons has often been an uncomfortable experience. The design and materials used do not provide the same comfort as some other brands or sizes. The tampons can feel bulky and even somewhat invasive, making it difficult to forget you're wearing them.Tampax Super Plus Tampons excel at preventing leaks. They have a well-thought-out design that ensures menstrual fluid is locked away, providing peace of mind and enabling you to go about your day without worrying about accidents.In conclusion, Tampax Super Plus Tampons are a reliable choice for managing heavy flow days. They offer superb absorption, comfortable fit, and leak protection, allowing you to feel confident and secure during your period. The ease of application, discretion, and range of sizes are added benefits. If you're looking for tampons that can handle the toughest flow with grace, Tampax Super Plus Tampons are a solid option. They've been a go-to for me during those heavy flow days, and I recommend them to anyone seeking reliable protection and comfort.
